examples.en: They were flailing their arms to drive away the insects.
James flailed about in the shallow water.
The bird's wings flailed the water.
The wounded animal lay on the ground, flailing helplessly.
examples.ru: Раненный зверь беспомощно бился на земле.

examples.en: He flailed wildly as she tried to hold him down.
examples.ru: Он бешено размахивал руками и ногами, а она пыталась не дать ему встать.

examples.en: He was wildly flailing about on the dance floor.
